data.description: Welcome to the Beach. Just a few short blocks to the wonderful pier area on IB. This home is well cared for and has a newer roof, newer tile floors, newer dual pane windows and remodeled kitchen and baths. The family room is not included in the square footage and could be a 4th bedroom instead of a family room.The home qualified for VA financing when purchased so room was done in workmanship like manner. recessed lighting throughout makes this a light and bright home! The large flat yard is perfect for an ADU as well. The yards, both front and back are a blank slate This would be a great home to start or end your home ownership experience!
